(1, 'Face Wash with Vitamin E & Canola Oil', 'SkinCare', 1399, 'Images/skincare.jpg', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f35764%2f35764_4.png%3fversion%3d1604996100&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f35764%2f35764_1.png%3fversion%3d1643798705&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f35764%2f35764.png%3fversion%3d1664442900&q=70', 'Essentials Face Wash with Vitamin E & Canola Oil is the very definition of no-nonsense cleansing. Through a purifying triple-action effect, it’s designed to rid the skin of make-up, daily impurities and dead skin, leaving it feeling cleansed, refreshed an', 'Cleanse daily, mornings and evenings, by applying to your wet face and gently massaging with fingertips. Rinse thoroughly with warm water. Use as needed. Avoid the eye area.', 'All Ingredients\r\nAQUA, SODIUM LAURETH SULFATE, COCAMIDOPROPYL BETAINE, GLYCERIN, LAURETH-3, SODIUM CHLORIDE, SODIUM LAUROYL SARCOSINATE, PHENOXYETHANOL, PARFUM, DMDM HYDANTOIN, DISODIUM EDTA, CANOLA OIL, CITRIC ACID, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE\r\n', 'With its caring formulations Essentials offers protection and nourishment for all ages and skin types. Offering you a complete skin care routine with multi vitamin complex to leave your skin feeling fresh, moisturised and cared for all day long.\n'),
(2, 'ProCeuticals Instant Peptide Ampoules', 'SkinCare', 11849, 'Images/skincare2.jpg', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f40880%2f40880_2.png%3fversion%3d1669188908&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f40880%2f40880_4.png%3fversion%3d1669188909&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f40880%2f40880_3.png%3fversion%3d1669188908&w=534&q=70', 'If you’ve experienced skin sagging and wrinkles, then it’s time for a targeted solution to restore skin’s youthful firmness. As we age, skin becomes thinner and less elastic, due to physiological changes and the breakdown of collagen and elastin.\r\nThis pr', 'Usage: use one ampoule daily, half in AM, half in PM. Step 1: Take out the ampoule, ampoule opener, plastic dropper, and small cap. Step 2: Place the ampoule opener on the ampoule, gently press', 'All Ingredients\r\nAQUA, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, BIS-PEG-18 METHYL ETHER DIMETHYL SILANE, METHYL GLUCETH-20, DIGLYCERIN, PEG-75, GLYCERIN, PANTHENOL, AMMONIUM ACRYLOYLDIMETHYLTAURATE/VP COPOLYMER, AVENA SATIVA KERNEL EXTRACT, PHENOXYETHANOL, PPG-26-BUTETH-26, CAES', 'NOVAGE. POWERED BY SCIENCE. EMPOWERING YOU TO BE YOUR BEST. NovAge offers a series of scientifically-advanced skin care ranges designed to correct and slow the signs of ageing.'),
(3, 'All-Over Make-Up Remover', 'SkinCare', 1269, 'Images/makeupremove.png', 'https://www.shessperfect.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/6bf0b91cf69fd0b6f587a8eba4104d2e.jpg', 'https://scontent.fcmb1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/95586963_154833699357895_6956993755547172864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=973b4a&_nc_ohc=1Hq9eE0Z__0AX8PpjCt&_nc_ht=scontent.fcmb1-2.fna&oh=00_AfB2bIv8euAzM2QyFJXN9XLdXLko0u9w9XyQ37O4JgrLyg&oe=63E0B941', 'https://image.isu.pub/160430173420-53d6dd7c16b69ae155b95eedc8be2f79/jpg/page_5.jpg', 'Water-based make up remover with hydrating ingredients gently cleans away all traces of make up quickly and efficiently, to leave skin feeling perfectly refreshed, soft and moisturised. Ideal for sensitive skin, eyes and contact lens wearers.', 'Saturate a cotton pad with eye makeup remover. A dual phase eye makeup remover works for most eye makeup. It combines the dissolving power of an oil-based . Hold the cotton pad against your closed eye for about 20 seconds, applying gentle pressure. Don\'t scrub your eye at all, just hold the pad in place. Use a downward motion to gently wipe off makeup.', 'AQUA, GLYCERIN, SODIUM CHLORIDE, DISODIUM COCOAMPHODIACETATE, POLYSORBATE 20, PHENOXYETHANOL, IMIDAZOLIDINYL UREA, SODIUM HYALURONATE, METHYLPARABEN, CITRIC ACID, PROPYLPARABEN, CHAMOMILLA RECUTITA FLOWER EXTRACT, ETHYLPARABEN', ''),
(4, 'Clarifying Toning Solution', 'SkinCare', 2990, 'Images/skincare10.png', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f41672%2f41672_3.png%3fversion%3d1629970202&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f41672%2f41672_2.png%3fversion%3d1629970201&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f41672%2f41672_1.png%3fversion%3d1629969301&w=534&q=70', 'Daily toner designed for oily, blemish-prone skin that targets and prevents blemishes, blackheads and enlarged pores. Contains Salicylic Acid (BHA) and Gluconolactone (PHA) that purify the skin and tighten pores, as well as a Soothing Complex that helps calm the skin. This effective mattifying toner also removes any last traces of impurities and reduces redness of blemish marks.', 'Use daily after cleansing. Apply toner to a cotton pad and sweep over face, avoiding the eye area.', 'AQUA, PROPANEDIOL, GLYCERIN, ALCOHOL DENAT., GLUCONOLACTONE, PEG-8, SODIUM CITRATE, SALICYLIC ACID, PANTHENOL, CITRIC ACID, OCIMUM BASILICUM FLOWER/LEAF EXTRACT, CAMELLIA SINENSIS LEAF EXTRACT, SODIUM BENZOATE, LACTIC ACID, POTASSIUM SORBATE', 'Pure Skin has a wide range of products to target spots and blackheads and help prevent breakouts. All Pure Skin products are anti-bacterial and have detect technology combined with salicylic acid to clear away dead skin cells, limit sebum production and prevent shine.'),
(5, 'Iconic Lipstick SPF 15', 'Make-Up', 3849, 'Images/makeup1.jpg', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f42324%2f42324_2.png%3fversion%3d1651610701&w=534&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?q=70&externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f42324%2f42324.png%3fversion%3d1651610700&w=534', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f42324%2f42324_3.png%3fversion%3d1651610701&w=534&q=70', 'Lasting, sumptuous hybrid lip colour in one glide, with a luminous satin finish that renews lip appearance, for a youth enhanced look and feel.\r\nExclusive blend of natural oils and extract help reduce visible signs of lip ageing while nourishing and smoothing the lips. SPF 15.', 'Line lips with Giordani Gold Lip Pencil for enhanced longevity and definition and place Giordani Gold Iconic Lipstick SPF 15 at the centre of the upper lip, moving outwards towards each corner. Repeat on bottom lip and continue adding lipstick tip to contour, define and shape lips.', 'All Ingredients\r\nOCTYLDODECANOL, BIS-DIGLYCERYL POLYACYLADIPATE-1, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRAISOSTEARATE, ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, PARAFFIN, CERA MICROCRISTALLINA, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRACAPRYLATE/TETRACAPRATE, SYNTHETIC WAX, MICA, OCTOCRYLENE, COPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA, HELIANTHUS ANNUUS SEED CERA, PARFUM, SHOREA ROBUSTA RESIN, RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA, GLYCERYL CAPRYLATE, PYRUS MALUS SEED OIL, SIMMONDSIA CHINENSIS SEED OIL, HELIANTHUS ANNUUS SEED OIL, POLYETHYLENE, BHT, ARGANIA SPINOSA KERNEL OIL, GERANIUM MACULATUM EXTRACT, MYOSOTIS SYLVATICA FLOWER/LEAF/STEM EXTRACT, ASCORBYL PALMITATE, TOCOPHEROL, +/-: CI 77891, CI 15850, CI 77492, CI 19140, CI 77499, CI 77491, CI 42090\r\n', 'For 40 years, Giordani Gold has strived to create beautiful, premium products infused with the world’s most exclusive raw ingredients. The quest for craftsmanship and perfection reflects our desire to help you live your life beautifully.\r\n'),
(6, 'THE Ordinary Multi-Peptide Serum for Hair Density', 'HairCare', 8950, 'Images/ordinary.png', 'https://theordinary.com/dw/image/v2/BFKJ_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-deciem-master/default/dw789dc51d/Images/products/The%20Ordinary/lifestyle/mas-rdn-multi-peptide-serum-for-hair-density-lifestyle.jpg?sw=1200&sh=1200&sm=fit', 'https://theordinary.com/dw/image/v2/BFKJ_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-deciem-master/default/dw703f7197/Images/products/The%20Ordinary/swatch/rdn-multi-peptide-serum-for-hair-density-60ml-swatch.png?sw=1200&sh=1200&sm=fit', 'https://cosmetics.lk/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/ord-013-01.png', 'This concentrated formula is designed to support hair health so that it looks thicker, denser, fuller, and healthier. The Ordinary Multi-Peptide Serum for hair density presents in this formula includes REDENSYL™ complex (with Larix Europaea Wood Extract and Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract), Procapil™ peptide complex, CAPIXYL™ peptide complex, BAICAPIL™ complex, AnaGain™ (Pisum Sativum Extract) and High-Solubility Caffeine (1% net Caffeine by weight), in an ultra-lightweight, emollient base for efficient penetration. The total concentration of these technologies in the formula by weight is 21.15%.', 'Apply a few drops or as needed once daily, ideally at bedtime, to clean dry scalp. Massage into scalp thoroughly. This formula is a leave-on/in treatment.\r\nDo not wash hair or scalp after application. If irritation occurs, cease use and consult a physician.\r\nUse only as directed on unbroken skin. Advised to do a patch test before use. Keep out of reach of children.', ' Caffeine, Biotinoyl Tripeptide-1, Acetyl Tetrapeptide-3, Larix Europaea Wood Extract, Pisum Sativum Extract, Scutellaria Baicalensis Root Extract, Triticum Vulgare Germ Extract, Glycine Soja Germ Extract, Trifolium Pratense Flower Extract, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract', 'Apply a small amount of the product onto a clean area of skin on the upper forearm.\nKeep the area dry.\nIf the product has a specified duration of use, rinse off after this time has elapsed. Otherwise, rinse off after 24 hours.'),
(7, 'Lacoste Magnetic Pour Elle Eau de Parfum 80ml', 'Fragrance', 18000, 'Images/perfume10.png', 'https://image1.lacoste.com/dw/image/v2/AAQM_PRD/on/demandware.static/Sites-INT-Site/Sites-master/en/dw015381d4/82463507_000_31.jpg?imwidth=915&impolicy=product', 'https://image1.lacoste.com/dw/image/v2/AAQM_PRD/on/demandware.static/Sites-INT-Site/Sites-master/en/dwdd5cb9c3/82463506_000_24.jpg?imwidth=915&impolicy=product', 'https://image1.lacoste.com/dw/image/v2/AAQM_PRD/on/demandware.static/Sites-INT-Site/Sites-master/en/dw79bd060b/82463507_000_32.jpg?imwidth=915&impolicy=product', 'Charm and elegance are effortlessly revealed naturally with this new perfume which plays on the desire to seduce and greatly enhances attraction.', 'take a shower or bath and dry your skin. Apply an unscented body lotion and/or Vaseline first. First perfume, then clothes. Spray perfume on your pulse points. Spray but don’t rub.', 'Linalool, Limonene, Coumarin, Citronellol, Benzyl Alcohol, Isoeugenol, Citral, Benzyl Benzoate, Hydroxycitronellal', 'Olfactory family: Oriental Floral\r\nTop notes: Sweet orange, Mango Accord\r\nHeart notes: Jasmine Accord, Rose Accord, Violet Leaves\r\nBase notes: Patchouli, Tonka Bean, Vanilla Accord'),
(8, 'NEUTROGENA Oil-Free Soothing Facial Cleanser', 'SkinCare', 4800, 'Images/skincare7.png', 'https://cosmetics.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/NE003-2-1-1-1-1-1-1-150x150.jpg', 'https://cosmetics.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/NE003-1-600x400.jpg', 'https://cosmetics.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/NE003-3-600x407.jpg', 'With naturally soothing aloe and chamomile, NEUTROGENA Oil-Free Acne Wash Redness Soothing Facial Cleanser’s unique formula powerfully clears away breakouts and also blackheads without over-drying.', 'Cleanse twice a day.\r\nApply NEUTROGENA Oil-Free Acne Wash Redness Soothing Facial Cleanser to hands, add water, and then work into a lather.\r\nMassage face gently.\r\nThen rinse thoroughly.\r\nHowever, skin irritation and dryness is more likely to occur if you use another topical medication at the same time. If irritation occurs, only use one topical medication at a time.\r\nAvoid contact with the eyes. If contact occurs, rinse thoroughly with water.', 'Water, Sodium C14-16 Olefin Sulfonate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, PEG-120 Methyl Glucose Dioleate, Sodium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Fragrance, PEG-80 Sorbitan Laurate, Disodium EDTA, Sodium Glycolate, Sodium Hydroxide, C12-15 Alkyl Lactate, Benzalkonium Chloride, Sodium Benzotriazolyl Butylphenol Sulfonate, Ethanol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Tetrasodium EDTA, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Citric Acid', 'This salicylic acid face wash visibly reduces the redness on your face as well as calms skin irritation that can be caused by acne, so, your skin looks and feels clearer and also healthier as a result with Neutrogena acne treatment. Discover further Neutrogena acne treatments for a complete acne face care routine.'),
(9, 'Victoria\'s Secret Bombshell Seduction Eau de Parfum', 'Fragrance', 23700, 'Images/perfume2.jpg', 'https://www.victoriassecret.com/p/760x1013/tif/c3/41/c3411de785a84379a8147b2389aae606/S21_BTY_202_531.jpg', 'https://www.victoriassecret.com/p/760x1013/tif/ed/ef/edeff1241d68449f9fdf57c95da0f6b2/111673803337_OF_F.jpg', 'https://www.victoriassecret.com/p/760x1013/tif/a8/e0/a8e0fd4a5b9848abbbb0dffb8d0db3da/SU20_BTY_048_e10538773.jpg', 'Mysterious and irresistible, Bombshell Seduction is an extension of  America’s No. 1 Fragrance.* Inspired by the beauty of our signature ribbon, our perfumers designed Bombshell Seduction to evoke the cool touch of satin on bare skin. French sage opens the fragrance with an airy, refreshing feel. An intoxicating duo of white florals make up the glowing floral heart: signature white peony and creamy tuberose. Velvet musk adds a whisper of skin-like warmth, a mysterious end-note to this sheer beauty.', 'Put 1-2 drops on your underwear, wrists, neck and nape to help you radiate a seductive. fragrance for a more romantic date.', 'Alcohol Denat., water, fragrance, propylene glycol, glycerin, butyl methoxydibenzoylmethane, Ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate, PPG-25-Buteth-26, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, PEG-40 hydrogenated castor oil, chamomilla Recutita flower extract, aloe barbadensis leaf extract, amyl cinnamal, benzyl alcohol', 'Fragrance type: Floral Warm\r\nNotes: white peony, sage, velvet musk\r\nEau de Parfum is our most concentrated, pure version of the fragrance\r\n100 ml/3.4 fl oz.\r\nDomestic'),
(10, 'MAYBELLINE ALL-IN-ONE EYE & CHEEK PALETTE', 'Make-Up', 5900, 'Images/eyeshadow.jpg', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/eye-shadow/the-city-kits-all-in-one-eye-and-cheek-palette/maybelline-eyeshadow-blush-bronzer-the-city-kits-eye-cheek-palette-pink-edge-041554545869-t.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=FD7FBA86FC91EC5F49699A59D6A74BAF6AD637FD', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/eye-shadow/the-city-kits-all-in-one-eye-and-cheek-palette/maybelline-eyeshadow-blush-bronzer-the-city-kits-eye-cheek-palette-pink-edge-041554545869-d.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=E31CD354CCE45B9758E631A95E83D2F9E47C7BBF', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/eye-shadow/the-city-kits-all-in-one-eye-and-cheek-palette/maybelline-eyeshadow-blush-bronzer-the-city-kits-eye-cheek-palette-pink-edge-041554545869-d2.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=8426C1EB68F11A0F063AF8DFD971DDAB4AADFADA', 'The City Kits All-in-One Eye & Cheek Highlighter palette brightens the eye area and highlights the cheek contours.', 'Step 1. Apply color from the eyelid to the brow bone.\r\n\r\nStep 2. Shade in the lid.\r\n\r\nStep 3. Add color to the inner corner.\r\n\r\nStep 4. Contour at the crease and line of the eye.\r\n\r\nStep 5. Apply highlighter.\r\n\r\nStep 6. Apply blush.', 'TALC, SYNTHETIC FLUORPHLOGOPITE, OCTYLDODECYL STEAROYL STEARATE, MAGNESIUM MYRISTATE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRAISOSTEARATE, CALCIUM SODIUM BOROSILICATE, STEARYL DIMETHICONE, NYLON-12, SILICA, ALUMINUM STARCH OCTENYLSUCCINATE, DIISOSTEARYL MALATE, ALUMINA, CALCIUM ALUMINUM BOROSILICATE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, DIMETHICONE, DEHYDROACETIC ACID, OCTADECENE, PHENOXYETHANOL, HEXYLENE GLYCOL, ISODODECANE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE, AQUA / WATER / EAU, MALTODEXTRIN, TIN OXIDE STEARIC ACID', 'From iridescent to edgy matte eyes, create an infinite number of makeup looks with these city inspired all in one makeup palettes. Each eye and cheek palette includes eight creamy eyeshadows, one blush, and one