(11, 'MAYBELLINE MASTER BLUSH COLOR & HIGHLIGHT KIT', 'Make-Up', 6400, 'Images/blush.jpg', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/face-makeup/blush-bronzer/facestudio-master-blush-color-and-highlight-kit/maybelline-blush-face-studio-master-blush-palette-041554496475-o.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=CB58873A0963D6337DC5E62B41837F2D35CAEC9B', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/face-makeup/blush-bronzer/facestudio-master-blush-color-and-highlight-kit/maybelline-blush-face-studio-master-blush-palette-041554496475-t.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=2532EF676D7B14CC9359923077D67C7F7BFD9989', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/face-makeup/blush-bronzer/facestudio-master-blush-color-and-highlight-kit/maybelline-blush-face-studio-master-blush-palette-041554496475-c.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=6F3CFCD208703004FE6BBFA0551EED65145C0D08', 'Facestudio® Master Blush Color & Highlight Kit delivers unlimited artistry in a beautifully curated collection of blushes and highlighter for a versatile cheek palette.', 'Step 1. Apply blush.\r\nTip: Use shades alone or mix & match shades to create your own look.\r\nStep 2. Add highlighter. Blend.', 'TALC\r\nSYNTHETIC FLUORPHLOGOPITE\r\nTRIISOSTEARIN\r\nPHENYL TRIMETHICONE\r\nMAGNESIUM STEARATE\r\nCAPRYLYL GLYCOL\r\nSILICA\r\nALUMINA\r\nCALCIUM ALUMINUM BOROSILICATE\r\nTIN OXIDE\r\nCALCIUM SODIUM BOROSILICATE\r\nMAGNESIUM SILICATE\r\n[+/- MAY CONTAIN / PEUT CONTENIR\r\nMICA\r\nCI 77891 / TITANIUM DIOXIDE\r\nCI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499 / IRON OXIDES\r\nCI 77007 / ULTRAMARINES', 'Go beyond the highlight for vibrant and dimensional statement cheeks. Maybelline\'s Color & Highlight Kit allows you to blush your own way. Use each shade alone or mix and match to create a custom cheek color.'),
(12, 'MAYBELLINE WASHABLE MASCARA MAKEUP', 'Make-Up', 3900, 'Images/mascara.jpg', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/mascara/lash-sensational-sky-high/very-black/maybelline-lash-sensational-sky-high-wsh-801-very-black-041554590500-t.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=93302492C5B1B3FE410939D4B76E4D8335A3CCCB', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/mascara/lash-sensational-sky-high/jobeauty_productinfo_lashsensational_skyhigh_mobile_375x562%20(1).jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=96AF7861A31DA2C165368CA692B4DCAD3B0083B1', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/global/eye-makeup/mascara/lash-sensational-sky-high/applicationmacro_productinfo_lashsensational_skyhigh_desktop_316x474.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=5BBD2CF1012F15CA71057F3BEB57CB92E8A5824F', 'Sky High lengthening and volume mascara for sky high lash impact from every angle. Long lasting mascara delivers full volume and limitless length.', 'For best results, hold Maybelline Lash Sensational Sky High mascara\'s flexible brush against lashes and extend from root to tip repeatedly until desired volume and length is achieved.', 'AQUA / WATER / EAU,\r\nPROPYLENE GLYCOL,\r\nSTYRENE/ACRYLATES/AMMONIUM METHACRYLATE COPOLYMER,\r\nPOLYURETHANE-35,\r\nCERA ALBA / BEESWAX / CIRE DABEILLE,\r\nSYNTHETIC FLUORPHLOGOPITE,\r\nGLYCERYL STEARATE,\r\nCETYL ALCOHOL,\r\nPEG-200 GLYCERYL STEARATE,\r\nETHYLENEDIAMINE/STEARYL DIMER DILINOLEATE COPOLYMER,\r\nCOPERNICIA CERIFERA CERA / CARNAUBA WAX / CIRE DE CARNAUBA,\r\nSTEARIC ACID,\r\nPALMITIC ACID,\r\nETHYLENE/VA COPOLYMER,\r\nALCOHOL DENAT.,\r\nPARAFFIN,\r\nAMINOMETHYL PROPANEDIOL,\r\nPHENOXYETHANOL,\r\nCAPRYLYL GLYCOL,\r\nGLYCERIN', 'Exclusive Flex Tower mascara brush bends to volumize and extend every single lash from root to tip. Washable mascara formula infused with bamboo extract and fibers for long, full and lightweight lashes, that don\'t flake or smudge. Available in Very Black and Blackest Black, Cosmic Black, and now True Brown.'),
(13, 'MATTE INK LIQUID LIPSTICK INTO THE ZODIAC', 'Make-Up', 3200, 'Images/lipstick.jpg', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/us/lips-makeup/lipstick/super-stay-matte-ink-liquid-lipstick/lover/lover_lightskintone1_lipmacro_ssmatteink_portrait_760x1130.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=C02EAA4B1DE36D465705EE7BE09B34B0856E3378', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/us/lips-makeup/lipstick/superstay-matte-ink-liquid-lipstick-into-the-zodiac/maybelline-lip-superstay-matte-ink-zodiac-edition-15-lover-cancer-041554071382-t.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=2C97C1A05EF843871522BC14DD65B356D475CD92', 'https://www.maybelline.com/~/media/mny/us/lips-makeup/lipstick/super-stay-matte-ink-liquid-lipstick/lover/lover_mediumskintone_lipmacro_ssmatteink_portrait_760x1130.jpg?thn=0&w=380&hash=838217BF8356C1EED6BC769349C11F23B14C998E', 'SuperStay Matte Ink™ Liquid Lipstick gives you a flawless matte finish in a range of super saturated shades.', 'Step 1. Apply liquid lipstick in the center of your upper lip and follow the contours of your mouth.\r\n\r\nStep 2. Glide the liquid lipstick across the entire bottom lip.\r\n\r\nStep 3. Allow product to dry.\r\n\r\nTip: For easy removal, use with Maybelline\'s SuperStay Eraser lipstick remover.\r\n', 'Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Isododecane, Nylon-611/Dimethicone Copolymer, Dimethicone Crosspolymer, C30-45 Alkyldimethylsilyl Polypropylsilsesquioxane, Lauroyl Lysine, Alumina, Silica Silylate, Phenoxyethanol, Disodium Stearoyl Glutamate, Calcium Sodium Borosilicate, Aluminum Hydroxide, Limonene, Silica, Caprylyl Glycol, Benzyl Benzoate, Tin Oxide, Benzyl Alcohol, Citronellol, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate, Magnesium Silicate, Parfum', 'This limited-edition collection brings bold lips and a flawless matte finish to every sign. Now you can collect the constellations for an all-day matte lip color. Available in all 12 zodiac signs: 6 Matte Ink shades that last up to 16 hours and 6 Ink Crayon shades that last up to 8 hours. These matte lipstick shades are inspired by the signs written in the stars, so you always feel beautiful and ready for anything.'),
(14, 'Guerlain Mon Guerlain Intense 100 ml Eau de Parfum', 'Fragrance', 32300, 'Images/perfume3.jpg', 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/gQMAAOSwnohgo~nn/s-l1600.jpg', 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/IlcAAOSwzElgo~ny/s-l1600.jpg', 'https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/--IAAOSwPtxgo~ns/s-l1600.jpg', 'Mon Guerlain Eau de Parfum Intense by Guerlain is a Amber Woody fragrance for women. Mon Guerlain Eau de Parfum Intense was launched in 2019. Mon Guerlain Eau de Parfum Intense was created by Thierry Wasser and Delphine Jelk. ', 'Spray perfume on your pulse points\r\nThe best spots to apply a perfume are your pulse points: the points that are warm and moist because your veins are closest to the skin on those places.\r\nWhere you apply a perfume will have an impact on how you and others experience it.', 'Alcohol, Parfum (Fragrance), Aqua (Water), Linalool, Limonene, Hydroxycitronellal, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Coumarin, Diethylamino Hydroxybenzoyl Hexyl Benzoate, Bht, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Butylene Glycol Dicaprylate/Dicaprate, Citral, Geraniol, Citronellol, Benzyl Alcohol, Anise Alcohol, Farnesol', 'Top notes are Lavender, Mandarin Orange and Bergamot; middle notes are Tahitian Vanilla, Madagascar Vanilla, iris, Jasmine Sambac and Rose; base notes are Coumarin, Patchouli, Licorice, Benzoin, Australian Sandalwood and White Musk.'),
(15, 'Revlon ALL IN ONE SHAMPOO', 'HairCare', 4990, 'Images/haircare2.png', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Uniqone-Shampoo-scaled.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/Revlon_UniqOne_Rutina-Banner_Square-copia-scaled.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/uniqone-celebrate-model-3.webp', 'Our All-in-one Professional Shampoo has been created to provide spectacular smoothness and frizz control for silky, shiny and manageable hair.\r\nThe new and improved formula brings vitality to the hair and improves its texture.', 'Apply some of the shampoo to damp hair, massage gently and rinse with plenty of water.\r\nRepeat if necessary.', 'AQUA/WATER/EAU, SODIUM LAURETH SULFATE, BETAINE, COCAMIDOPROPYL BETAINE, PEG-7 GLYCERYL COCOATE, DECYL GLUCOSIDE, PEG-3 DISTEARATE, AMODIMETHICONE, C12-14 PARETH-12, CITRIC ACID, DISODIUM EDTA, GUAR HYDROXYPROPYLTRIMONIUM CHLORIDE, PANTHENOL, PEG-150 PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRASTEARATE, PEG-6 CAPRYLIC/CAPRIC GLYCERIDES, QUATERNIUM-22, PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, BENZYL SALICYLATE, CITRONELLOL, HEXYL CINNAMAL, LINALOOL, BENZYL ALCOHOL', '- Professional Results\r\n- Vegan Formula\r\n- Bottle made from 35% rPET\r\n- Dermatologically tested'),
(16, 'RADIANCE ARGAN SHAMPOO', 'HairCare', 5900, 'Images/haircare3.png', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/oro-fluido-shampoo-packshot-scaled-1.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/oro-fluido-shampoo-hand-texture.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/oro-fluido-full-range-2.webp', 'The Orofluido™ Radiance Shampoo is infused with argan oil is a moisturizing shampoo that smooths the hair leaving it shiny and delicately scented with our signature fragrance.', '1. Apply the Orofluido™ Radiance Shampoo to wet hair, massage gently and rinse thoroughly.\r\n2. In addition to the Radiance Shampoo infused with argan oil, use the full Orofluido™ range to indulge yourself in a complete mindful ritual.\r\n3. Vegan formula.', 'Aqua/Water/Eau, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Betaine, Decyl Glucoside, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Benzotriazolyl Dodecyl p-Cresol, Citric Acid, Disodium EDTA, Lauric Acid, Lauryl Alcohol Diphosphonic Acid, Methoxy PEG/PPG-7/3 Aminopropyl Dimethicone, Panthenol, PEG-12 Dimethicone, PEG-150 Pentaerythrityl Tetrastearate, PEG-6 Caprylic/Capric Glycerides, PEG-60 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Polyquaternium-10, Sodium Acetate, Sodium Chloride, Tocopheryl Acetate, Parfum (Fragrance)', 'Feel the enveloping texture of the new Orofluido’s transparent-golden shampoo. It will moisturize and smooth hair leaving it shiny and delicately scented.\r\n\r\n'),
(17, 'EKSPERIENCE BOOST PHASE 0 SCALP PREP', 'HairCare', 7900, 'Images/haircare4.png', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/eksperience-boost-volumizing-booster-doose-2-530x530.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/eksperience-boost-volumizing-booster-doose-3.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/eksperience-boost-volumizing-booster-doose-3.webp', 'An exfoliator for deep cleaning the scalp.', 'Apply scalp exfoliator onto dry scalp and massage gently, then rinse thoroughly. Proceed with the next treatment.\r\nFrequency of use in the salon: if associated with a specific anomaly, once per week for 6 weeks twice a year.\r\nFrequency of use at home: before each wash (hair cleanser) or treatment.', 'Aqua (Water (Eau)), Hydroxyethylcellulose, Panthenol, Ethoxydiglycol, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Propanediol, Hydroxyacetophenone, Butylene Glycol, Bis-Cetearyl Amodimethicone, Glycerin, Sodium Lactate, Hydrolyzed Rhodophycea Extract, Glycolic Acid, Hydrolyzed Actin, Maris Aqua (Sea Water (Eau De Mer)), Sucrose, Urea, Sodium Citrate, Ceteareth- 7, Ceteareth-25, Undaria Pinnatifida Extract, Tartaric Acid, Malic Acid, Fucus Vesiculosus Extract, Propylene Glycol, Parfum (Fragrance), Limonene, Benzyl Alcohol.', 'Cleanses, purifies and prepares the scalp to receive any of the Eksperience™ beauty rituals.'),
(18, 'EKSPERIENCE SUN PRO MARINE SUN PROTECTION HAIR CREAM', 'HairCare', 4500, 'Images/haircare5.png', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/eksperience-sun-pro-water-base-hair-wax-2.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/eksperience-sun-pro-water-base-hair-wax-3.webp', 'https://www.revlonprofessional.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/eksperience-purifying-cream-6.webp', 'This moisturizing hair cream is formulated to nourish the hair while being exposed to the sun.', 'Pour a small amount of the Marine Protective coconut oil leave-in hair treatment into your hands and massage through damp lengths and ends.\r\nDo not rinse. For maximum protection, reapply as often as necessary.', 'Aqua/Water/Eau, Butylene Glycol, Alcohol Denat., Cyclopentasiloxane, Dimethicone, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Isopropyl Myristate, 1,2-Hexanediol, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, BHT, C13-14 Isoparaffin, Caprylyl Glycol, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Dimethiconol, Fucus Vesiculosus Extract, Glycerin, Hydrolyzed Actin, Hydrolyzed Corallina Officinalis Extract, Laureth-7, Macadamia Ternifolia Seed Oil, Maris Aqua/Sea Water/Eau De Mer, Polyacrylamide, Propylene Glycol, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Benzophenone-3, Parfum (Fragrance), Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Coumarin, Limonene, Linalool, Phenoxyethanol', 'Sun protection hair cream nourishes and moisturizes the hair during sun exposure.'),
(19, 'CREED WIND FLOWERS PERFUME', 'Fragrance', 33000, 'Images/perfume4.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/3298/5441/products/image_200x.jpg?v=1648211878', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/3298/5441/products/image_f93bd507-16fe-4ccc-bfe1-659772658260_650x.jpg?v=1648211878', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0271/3298/5441/products/MicrosoftTeams-image_3_200x.png?v=1648211878', 'Inspired by movement, Wind Flowers is the latest women\'s perfume from the House of Creed. Floral and fresh, this fragrance opens with sweet jasmine, wrapped around the zesty scent of Tunisian orange blossom and softened by a fresh and a fruity peach note, a powerful heart of delicate jasmine flower, tuberose petals and a soft rose extract add depth and texture to this fragrance while a warm flurry of sandalwood is twisted around a haze of iris and musk. ', 'Apply an unscented body lotion and/or Vaseline first.\r\nFirst perfume, then clothes. \r\nSpray perfume on your pulse points. \r\nSpray but don\'t rub. \r\nDon\'t overdo it.\r\nSpritz, don\'t mist.\r\nComb it in your hair.', 'ALCOHOL / PARFUM (FRAGRANCE)/ AQUA (WATER)/ ETHYLHEXYL SALICYLATE/ BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE/ PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE', 'A vibrant note of orange blossom and creamy praline offsets this dusky floral scent; bringing to life this luminous fragrance for her.'),
(20, 'MESAUDA WOW!GLOW HIGHLIGHTER', 'Make-Up', 8900, 'Images/highlight.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/WOW_GLOW-Palette-Illuminanti-Compatti-1667563628_540x.jpg?v=1667563630', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/WOW_GLOW-Palette-Illuminanti-Compatti-1667563642_2000x.jpg?v=1667563644', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/WOW_GLOW-Palette-Illuminanti-Compatti-1667563647_2000x.jpg?v=1667563649', 'Wow!Glow is the palette of Highlighters in 4 colours, to create infinite looks and enhance every complexion. The hybrid cream-powder texture blends perfectly into the skin leaving sophisticated, shimmering highlights on the face.', 'Create your perfect base using your usual products. Use the F07 flame brush and apply highlighter to prominent areas of the face: cheekbones, cupid\'s bow, inner corner of the eye, back of the eye and tip of the nose. You can overlap several shades.', 'SYNTHETIC FLUORPHLOGOPITE, DIMETHICONE, TALC, ZINC STEARATE, OCTYLDODECYL STEAROYL STEARATE, MICA, DIISOSTEARYL MALATE, TRIMETHYLSILOXYSILICATE, POLYMETHYLSILSESQUIOXANE, DIMETHICONE CROSSPOLYMER, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, HEXYLENE GLYCOL, PHENOXYETHANOL, CI 77891/TITANIUM DIOXIDE', 'If you want a subtle shimmer effect, apply highlighter with fan brush F10. If you want a more radiant effect, apply directly with your fingers.'),
(21, 'MESAUDA SUBLIMATTE LIPSTICK', 'Make-Up', 2500, 'Images/lips.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/SUBLIMATTE---UNLIMITED-MESAUDA-1667484628_2000x.jpg?v=1667484630', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/SUBLIMATTE---UNLIMITED-MESAUDA-1667484640_2000x.jpg?v=1667484642', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/SUBLIMATTE---UNLIMITED-MESAUDA-1667484643_540x.jpg?v=1667484645', 'A liquid texture with a matte finish, no-transfer properties and tested to last up to 18 hours. Thanks to the formula enriched with special raw materials, the product stays thin on the lips for a silky, weightless finish.', 'Using the tip of the special heart-shaped applicator, spread the product starting from the center of the upper lip toward the outer corners, with the flattest part filling in the remaining central part. Then repeat on the lower lip.', 'ISODODECANE, TRIMETHYLSILOXYSILICATE, DIMETHICONE, TRISILOXANE, ISONONYL ISONONANOATE, CI 77891/TITANIUM DIOXIDE, MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX/MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX, MICA, CETYL DIMETHICONE, DIMETHICONE/VINYL DIMETHICONE CROSSPOLYMER, CI 77491/IRON OXIDES, CI 77492/IRON OXIDES', 'Liquid lipstick with a matte finish, no-transfer properties and tested to last up to 18 hours. Thanks to the formula enriched with special raw materials, the product stays thin on the lips for a silky, weightless finish. Thanks to the high amount of pigment within the formula, the color is full from the first swipe, plus spreading is made easy thanks to the special heart-shaped applicator, which deposits the product evenly and allows you to define the edge of the lips with precision, without having to use a pencil.'),
(22, '+Rose Radiance Perfector', 'SkinCare', 5990, 'Images/roseradiance.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/RoseRadiancePerfector_1_-JAN21_large.jpg?v=1663353103', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/Rose-Radiance-Lotion-Swatch-29OCT20-web_large.jpg?v=1663353103', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/Rose-Radiance-Perfector-with-Box-24OCT20-web_large.jpg?v=1663353103', 'Delicately tinted, Rose-infused complexion enhancer blurs and brightens to give skin a fresh finish. This radiance perfector is formulated to instantly enliven the face with a pearlescent finish for a healthy glow.', '• Use daily, or as often as needed.\r\n• Step 1: Apply coin-sized amount onto cheekbone, browbone and cupid\'s bow to enhance features.\r\n• Pro Tip: Use all over as a radiance-enhancing priming lotion and for a tone-correcting effect.', 'Aqua/Water/Eau, Propanediol, Etylhexyl Palmitate, Mica, Diphenylsiloxy Phenyl Trimethicone, Diisostearyl Malate, Steareth-21, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Squalane, Panthenol, Rosa Damascena Flower Water, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Rosa Rubiginosa Seed Oil, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ceramide NP, Pelargonium Graveolens Oil, Hydroxyethyl Acrylate/Sodium Acryloyldimethyl Taurate Copolymer, Polysorbate 20, Sorbitan Isostearate, Cetyl Dimethicone, Hydroxyacetophenone', '\"Sheer rosy face lotion to highlight and add a pearlescent glow\" - Petra\r\n• Sheer rosy tint brightens & corrects\r\n• Blurs imperfections\r\n• Instantly imparts a youthful glow\r\n• Suitable for all skin types'),
(23, 'Glow Tonic 100ml', 'SkinCare', 7890, 'Images/tonic.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/GlowTonic-100ml_1_-JUL2021_large.jpg?v=1664563642', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/GlowTonic_100ml_SugarCane_large.jpg?v=1664563642', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1463/5858/products/glowtonic-100ml-may19_3_f5565c8e-138d-44c7-880e-e73e6e5fc131_large.jpg?v=1664563642', 'The Pixi Glow Tonic 100ml miracle working toner helps brighten the complexion resulting in a healthier glow.', '• Use: Either in the AM and PM or when needed.\r\n• Step 1: Cleanse your face.\r\n• Step 2: Saturate a cotton pad with the Glow Tonic and sweep across face, neck and décolletage (avoiding the eye area).\r\n• Step 3: Follow with a serum or moisturizer.', 'Aqua/Water/Eau, Glycolic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide, Butylene Glycol, Glycerin, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Hamamelis Virginiana (Witch Hazel)Water, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract, Hexylene Glycol, Fructose, Glucose, Sucrose, Urea, Dextrin, Alanine, Glutamic Acid, Aspartic Acid,Hexyl Nicotinate, Panax Ginseng Root Extract, Ethylhexylglycerin, Disodium EDTA, Biotin, Panthenol, PPG-26-Buteth-26, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil,Phenoxyethanol, Parfum/Fragrance, Caramel, Benzyl Benzoate', '• Formulated with 5% Glycolic Acid.\r\n• Exfoliates, brightens and smooths skin.\r\n• Aloe Vera, Ginseng and Botanical extracts work together to nourish and treat.\r\n• Instant glow enhancer.\r\n• Alcohol-free\r\n• Suitable for all skin types\r\n• Paraben-free\r\n• Not tested on animals'),
(24, 'Hydrate Shampoo', 'HairCare', 3990, 'Images/haircare6.png', 'https://media.ulta.com/i/ulta/2565096cm_alt01?w=720&fmt=webp', 'https://media.ulta.com/i/ulta/2565096cm_alt04?w=720&fmt=webp', 'https://media.ulta.com/i/ulta/2565096cm_alt03?w=720&fmt=webp', 'Pureology\'s Hydrate Shampoo is a creamy, sulfate-free shampoo that deeply hydrates normal to thick dry, color-treated hair.', 'Apply a dime-sized amount to wet hair at the scalp. Lather and work down to the ends. Rinse. For extra cleansing, repeat.', 'Aqua/Water/Eau, Sodium Cocoyl Isethionate, Disodium Laureth, Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Sodium Lauroyl, Sarcosinat, Glycol Distearate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycereth-26, Decyl Glucoside, Coconut Acid, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Isethionate, Parfum/Fragrance, Citric Acid, Ppg-5-Ceteth-20, Divinyldimethicone/Dimethicone Copolymer, Sodium Chloride, Polyquaternium-7, Amodimethicone, Coco-Betaine, Polyquaternium-10, Propylene Glycol, Peg-55 Propylene Glycol Oleate, Linalool, Carbomer, C11-15 Pareth-7, Benzoic Acid, Laureth-9, Butylene Glycol, Glycerin', 'Provides superior moisture\r\nGives hair touchable softness\r\nProvides extraordinary color protection\r\nHighly concentrated formula allows for 75+ shampoos in a single bottle\r\nContains less than 1% of synthetic fragrances\r\nThis product is 100% vegan\r\nRecyclable packaging'),
(25, 'Acqua di Gioia', 'Fragrance', 23900, 'Images/perfume5.png', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p271538-av-1-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p271538-av-2-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p271538-av-5-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'Inspired by Italy’s Mediterranean coast, this Giorgio Armani perfume for women is a singular blend of serenity and exhilaration. Opening up with the clean, fresh perfume of citrus, the eau de parfum reveals a heart of intoxicating jasmine fragrance and lingers with a scent of warm cedarwood.\r\n', '-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting, stronger scent. \r\n-After applying, avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance, causing it to wear off more quickly. \r\n-If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists, be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing, as this tends to rinse off the scent. \r\n-Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent.', 'Alcohol, Parfum / Fragrance, Aqua / Water, Limonene, Benzyl Salicylate, Benzyl Alcohol, Hydroxycitronellal, Citronellol, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Hexyl Cinnamal, Ethylhexyl Salicylate, Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane, Linalool, Geraniol, Citral, Benzyl Benzoate, Cinnamal, Methyl-2-Octynoate, Eugenol, Ci 61570 / Green 5, Ci 17200 / Red 33.', 'Fragrance Family: Fresh\r\nScent Type: Fresh Aquatics\r\nKey Notes: Jasmine, Gardenia, Warm Woods\r\n'),
(26, 'NINA RICCI L\'AIR DU TEMPS', 'Fragrance', 19990, 'Images/perfume8.png', 'https://images.prismic.io/nina-ricci/68e1a786-e445-4069-b9d1-7a7526820bf6_ADT_EDT_10916_NINA_RICCI_ATOUBIANA7171_eautoilette_V6_RESPONSIVE.jpg?q=60&auto=compress,format&fit=max&config[deviceSizes]=160,320,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&config[imageSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,256,384&config[path]=&config[loader]=imgix&config[allSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,160,256,320,384,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&width=640', 'https://images.prismic.io/nina-ricci/3973cc50-2fbc-4531-bfcc-12ff554dcab4_NINA_ADT2219.jpg?q=60&auto=compress,format&fit=max&config[deviceSizes]=160,320,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&config[imageSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,256,384&config[path]=&config[loader]=imgix&config[allSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,160,256,320,384,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&width=640', 'https://images.prismic.io/nina-ricci/90da6cf2-43b0-4d2c-9da1-011219949666_NINA_ADT2213.jpg?q=60&auto=compress,format&fit=max&config[deviceSizes]=160,320,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&config[imageSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,256,384&config[path]=&config[loader]=imgix&config[allSizes]=16,32,48,64,96,128,160,256,320,384,640,750,828,1080,1440,1940&width=640', 'Composed during the joyful time that followed the war, the fresh scent blends jasmine, rose and carnation, celebrating the essence of femininity with pure optimism.', 'Generously mist L\'Air du Temps Eau de Toilette onto your skin for a joyfully floral and spicy sillage.', 'ALCOHOL DENAT., AQUA (WATER), PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), BENZYL SALICYLATE, HYDROXYCITRONELLAL, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, LINALOOL, EUGENOL, BENZYL BENZOATE, AMYL CINNAMAL, LIMONENE, ISOEUGENOL, CITRONELLOL, FARNESOL, GERANIOL, HEXYL CINNAMAL, CITRAL, BENZYL ALCOHOL, DISODIUM EDTA, CI 19140 (YELLOW 5), CI 14700 (RED 4).', 'Representing peace and love, two doves are tenderly interlaced on the stopper.'),
(27, 'Dolce Eau de Parfum', 'Fragrance', 21990, 'Images/perfume9.png', 'https://dolcegabbana-view.thron.com/api/xcontents/resources/delivery/getThumbnail/dolcegabbana/400x0/0ec1c5ba-3d66-436e-b77c-5dbb6a8306f9.jpg?v=42&scalemode=manual', 'https://dolcegabbana-view.thron.com/api/xcontents/resources/delivery/getThumbnail/dolcegabbana/400x0/284df8cd-e823-48ab-8d79-5584d3a314bb.jpg?v=42&scalemode=manual', 'https://dolcegabbana-view.thron.com/api/xcontents/resources/delivery/getThumbnail/dolcegabbana/400x0/04a5e4dc-d2b6-4a87-8839-f3514d8c6783.jpg?v=42&scalemode=manual', 'Dolce&Gabbana Dolce Eau de Parfum is a perfume with an unmistakable, personal touch. Fresh and feminine, it embodies the delicate balance between innovation and craftsmanship which distinguishes the art of perfumed composition.\r\n', 'Apply an unscented body lotion and/or Vaseline first.\r\nFirst perfume, then clothes. \r\nSpray perfume on your pulse points.\r\nSpray but don\'t rub.', 'ALCOHOL, PARFUM (FRAGRANCE), AQUA (WATER), BENZYL SALICYLATE, ALPHA-ISOMETHYL IONONE, LINALOOL, ETHYLHEXYL METHOXYCINNAMATE, HEXYL CINNAMAL, HYDROXYCITRONELLAL, CITRONELLOL, DIETHYLAMINO HYDROXYBENZOYL HEXYL BENZOATE, LIMONENE, GERANIOL, BENZYL BENZOATE,\r\nISOEUGENOL, BENZYL ALCOHOL, CITRAL, BHT, CI 42090 (BLUE 1), CI 19140 (YELLOW 5), CI 60730 (EXT. VIOLET 2).', 'Dolce&Gabbana Dolce Eau de Parfum: a fresh and feminine fragrance.\r\n\r\nThe fragrance was created by Jean-Pierre Mary exclusively for Dolce&Gabbana.'),
(28, 'Olaplex No. 7 Bonding Hair Oil', 'Haircare', 10090, 'Images/haircare7.png', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p447376-av-02-zoom.jpg?imwidth=48', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p447376-av-03-zoom.jpg?imwidth=48', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/product/p447376-av-08-zoom.jpg?imwidth=48', 'Works by finding single sulfur hydrogen bonds and crosslinking them back together to form disulfide bonds; disulfide bonds are broken via chemical, thermal, and mechanical processes including brushing and combing the hair; gives hair superior strength by repairing broken disulfide bonds; and anti-breakage properties.', '-To dispense: Remove cap. Turn bottle upside down and gently tap index finger on the bottom of bottle to dispense a metered drop.\r\n-Apply a small amount to damp or dry hair, style as desired.\r\n-Tips: Add a few drops to No. 6 for incredible shine.', 'Dimethicone, Isohexadecane, C13-14 Isoparaffin, Coco-Caprylate, Phenyl Trimethicone, Bis-Aminopropyl Diglycol Dimaleate, Propanediol, Zea Mays (Corn) Oil, Beta-Carotene, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Moringa Oleifera Seed Oil, Punica Granatum Seed Oil, Water (Aqua), Morinda Citrifolia Fruit Powder, Fragrance (Parfum), Hexyl Cinnamal, Eclipta Prostrata Extract, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Limonene, Tocopherol, Citral, Linalool, Melia Azadirachta Leaf Extract, Citronellol, Pseudozyma Epicola/Camellia Sinensis Seed (Green Tea)', 'What it is: An ultra-lightweight, reparative, styling oil that increases shine, softness, and color vibrancy, while minimizing flyaways and protecting hair against heat damage.\r\n\r\nHair Texture: Fine, Medium, and Thick\r\n\r\nHair Benefits: Protects Colors, Fights Frizz, and Provides Heat Protection'),
(29, 'Vegamour GRO Hair Serum for Thinning Hai', 'HairCare', 18500, 'Images/haircare8.png', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2473064-av-20-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2473064-av-06-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'https://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s2473064-av-21-zoom.jpg?imwidth=612', 'A highly effective vegan serum that increases the appearance of hair density while reducing signs of shedding to promote thicker, fuller looking hair with clinically proven results in as little as 90 days.', '-Fill dropper.\r\n-Apply one dropperful directly onto dry or damp scalp.\r\n-Leave in.\r\n-Style as usual.\r\n-For best results, use daily.', 'Aqua, Butylene Glycol, Glycerin, Alcohol Denat., Caffeine, Polysorbate 20, Curcuma Longa (Turmeric) Callus Conditioned Media, Citrus Bergamia Peel Oil Expressed, Disodium Edta, Limonene, Trifolium Pratense Sprout Extract, Vigna Radiata Sprout Extract, Sodium Benzoate, Linalool, Potassium Sorbate, Gluconolactone, Biotin, Citral, Oligopeptide-2, Hexapeptide-40 Sh-Polypeptide 9, Hexapeptide-40 Sh-Polypeptide-86.', '- Reduces signs of hair thinning for thicker, fuller, longer looking hair\r\n- Most effective as a spot treatment\r\n- No visible residue and will not make hair greasy\r\n'),
(30, 'MESAUDA AT FIRST BLUSH', 'Make-Up', 5900, 'Images/blush.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/AT-FIRST-BLUSH-Blush-compatto-1665044961_540x.jpg?v=1668789393', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/AT-FIRST-BLUSH-Blush-compatto-1665044998_2000x.jpg?v=1668789393', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/AT-FIRST-BLUSH-Blush-compatto-1665044991_540x.jpg?v=1668789393', 'Compact, silky blush with a velvety touch that enhances the natural complexion. An extremely thin and light film thanks to the innovative technology of micronised pigments which allows the product to adhere better to the skin. The natural spherical polymers, on the other hand, improve skin-feel and have absorbent properties. A blush rich in active ingredients; a veritable pool of natural extracts that improve the elasticity of the skin: rose hip with its emollient and soothing action and Ginko biloba with its antioxidant properties.', 'apply a small amount of product with the round brush on the cheekbones, from the cheeks towards the temples, and vice versa. To sculpt, apply with the F05 oblique brush under the cheekbone, following the shape of the cheekbone from the centre of the face outwards.', 'TALC, MICA, ZEA MAYS (CORN) STARCH, CI 77491/IRON OXIDES, DIMETHICONE, CI 77891/TITANIUM DIOXIDE, OCTYLDODECYL STEAROYL STEARATE, ZINC STEARATE, PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRAISOSTEARATE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, ETHYLHEXYLGLYCERIN, CI 77007/ULTRAMARINES, CI 15850/RED 7 LAKE, ZEA MAYS OIL/ZEA MAYS (CORN) OIL, CI 77492/IRON OXIDES, CI 77499/IRON OXIDES, TIN OXIDE, GINKGO BILOBA EXTRACT/GINKGO BILOBA LEAF EXTRACT, ROSA CANINA FRUIT EXTRACT.', 'Velvety smooth and delicate texture;\r\nEasy application, adheres perfectly to the skin. Modular and long-wearing;\r\nNatural, satin finish and imperceptible;\r\nGinkgo biloba extract with antioxidant action, rose hip with emollient and soothing action.');
