(31, 'MESAUDA GLAM\'EYES', 'Make-Up', 6990, 'Images/eyeshadow1.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/GLAM-EYES-MESAUDA-1670419943_2000x.jpg?v=1670419945', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/GLAM-EYES-MESAUDA-1670419934_2000x.jpg?v=1670419936', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0584/8275/3705/products/GLAM-EYES-MESAUDA-1670419938_2000x.jpg?v=1670419940', 'Glam\'Eyes is a 12-colour eyeshadow palette in three different textures with extraordinary writing power and sensorial qualities. You can create ever-changing looks by choosing from a variety of matt, shimmer and duo-chrome textures and colours, and by balancing cool and warm tones.', 'Take a small amount of light-coloured eyeshadow with the E03/E04 flat bristle brush and apply to the entire eyelid, taking care to remove any excess powder on the back of the hand. To define the crease of the eyelid, apply a medium-coloured eyeshadow with the E01/E02 blending brush in circular movements. Apply and blend dark-coloured eyeshadows along the upper and lower lashline to give depth to the eyes. Apply shimmer eyeshadow to the centre of the eyelid for a 3D effect. Apply duo-chrome eyeshadow with your fingers for an ultra-shimmery effect.', 'CHIC - STYLISH - VOGUE - POSH: MICA, ZEA MAYS STARCH (ZEA MAYS (CORN) STARCH), SILICA, DIMETHICONE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL, OCTYLDODECANOL, STEARYL STEARATE, CETYL PALMITATE, STEARYL PALMITATE, CETYL STEARATE, CERA ALBA (BEESWAX), METHICONE, MICROCRYSTALLINE WAX, BEHENIC ACID, STEARIC ACID. +/- (MAY CONTAIN): CI 77891/TITANIUM DIOXIDE, CI 16035/RED 40 LAKE, CI 77491/IRON OXIDES, CI 77492/IRON OXIDES, CI 42090/BLUE 1 LAKE, CI 77499/IRON OXIDES. ROMANCE: MICA, ZINC STEARATE, DIMETHICONE, OCTYLDODECYL STEAROYL STEARATE, CAPRYLYL GLYCOL', '- Matt, shimmer and duo-chrome textures;\r\n\r\n- Warm and cool tones;\r\n\r\n- Writing and sensorial.\r\n\r\nCruelty free. Paraben-free formula.'),
(32, 'PHYTO CORRECTIVE GEL', 'SkinCare', 17500, 'Images/phyto.png', 'https://static.thcdn.com/images/large/original//productimg/1600/1600/11289629-1544892771938209.jpg', 'https://scontent.fcmb1-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/95311914_2870967339648501_6681236024552587264_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=973b4a&_nc_ohc=se_rHexDM8gAX-_2_ZW&_nc_ht=scontent.fcmb1-2.fna&oh=00_AfDI25p5PUe2DiMJX5bJv0UBikcWKl1tGftt5Gc1vnn8mg&oe=63E0976F', 'https://people.com/thmb/nSH46DCbFOq6CZIMluVZoCVIf0I=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(314x389:316x391)/kristen-bell-corrective-gel-554592ccf0b84abfb37f1c526c3a7925.jpg', 'A hydrating, soothing gel serum with botanical ingredients ideal to calm and hydrate skin while improving visual redness', 'As needed, apply 2-3 drops to face, neck, and chest. Can be used on other areas of the body as needed. If using in the morning, apply after a SkinCeuticals vitamin C antioxidant serum and before a SkinCeuticals sunscreen. If using with a retinol at night, apply after retinol application.', 'AQUA / WATER / EAU, GLYCERIN, PROPYLENE GLYCOL, POLYSORBATE 80, PHENOXYETHANOL, SODIUM BENZOATE, SODIUM HYALURONATE, HYDROXYETHYLCELLULOSE, DISODIUM EDTA, OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) LEAF EXTRACT, PARFUM / FRAGRANCE, BENZOPHENONE-4, BUTYLENE GLYCOL, CITRUS GRANDIS EXTRACT / GRAPEFRUIT FRUIT EXTRACT, CUCUMIS SATIVUS FRUIT EXTRACT / CUCUMBER FRUIT EXTRACT, BENZYL BENZOATE, CI 19140 / YELLOW 5,THYMUS VULGARIS FLOWER/LEAF EXTRACT - THYME FLOWER/LEAF EXTRACT, EUCALYPTUS GLOBULUS LEAF OIL, BENZYL ALCOHOL', 'Phyto Corrective Gel contains hyaluronic acid, cucumber, thyme, and other botanical ingredients, making it an ideal moisturizer for sensitive skin. It also features mulberry to help minimize the appearance of discoloration and promote a clear, fresh-looking complexion. This soothing gel is also an excellent moisturizer for acne-prone skin.'),
(33, 'Innocent White Lilac Perfumed Hand Cream', 'BathAndBody', 3500, 'Images/bath.png', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f43672%2f43672_2.png%3fversion%3d1615473090&w=60&h=60&bc=white&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f43672%2f43672_3.png%3fversion%3d1615473091&w=60&h=60&bc=white&q=70', 'https://media-asia-cdn.oriflame.com/productImage/?externalMediaId=product-management-media%2f43672%2f43672_4.png%3fversion%3d1615473091&w=60&h=60&bc=white&q=70', 'Pamper your hands with a cream that lingers the intoxicating scent of white lilacs in full bloom. This moisturising hand cream leaves the skin perfectly soft, smooth and delicately scented with a floral and feminine fragrance.', 'Squeeze a small amount of cream on your hands and massage into skin. Use throughout the day.', 'AQUA, GLYCERIN, ETHYLHEXYL PALMITATE, CETYL ALCOHOL, STEARYL ALCOHOL, PARFUM, GLYCERYL STEARATE SE, IMIDAZOLIDINYL UREA, METHYLPARABEN, CETEARETH-20, PRUNUS AMYGDALUS DULCIS OIL, CARBOMER, PROPYLPARABEN, STEARIC ACID, PALMITIC ACID, BENZYL SALICYLATE, SODIUM HYDROXIDE, LINALOOL, HYDROXYCITRONELLAL, TOCOPHERYL ACETATE, LIMONENE', 'A captivating, heady fragrance, evoking images of a resplendent garden at dawn’s crisp light. The floral, musky, white lilac scent opens with a blend of dewy Green Leaves, followed by a powdery heart of White Lilac, Watery Jasmine and Peony Petal, to finally settle on a velvety, woody Heliotrope base.'),
(34, 'Malibu Made Body Scrub', 'BathAndBody', 3400, 'Images/bodyscrub.png', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2098/5213/products/2_2048x2048.jpg?v=1627507171', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2098/5213/products/4-22_2048x2048.jpg?v=1627507331', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2098/5213/products/5_2048x2048.jpg?v=1627507331', 'All natural vanilla brown sugar body exfoliator that gently removes dead skin cells and replenishes the skin with hydrating organic oils and food-grade vanilla', 'Scrub body lovingly in circular motions before rinsing. Can be used before or during shower or bath. ', 'Brown sugar, coconut oil*, sweet almond oil*, jojoba seed oil*, glyceryl behenate/eicosadioate, natural flavor, castor oil, glyceryl caprylate, and glyceryl undecylenate.', 'Scented with food grade vanilla flavors, the Malibu Made Body Scrub smells like a fresh baked cookie.  '),
(35, 'Amethyst Exfoliating Body Scrub', 'BathAndBody', 6590, 'Images/scrub2.png', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81yZj37eaSL.jpg', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0203/8454/products/Herbivore_AmethystBodyPolish_Main_450x450.jpg?v=1591819858', 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0203/8454/products/Herbivore_Amethyst_Body_Scrub_Texture.jpg?v=1633716656', 'Reveal silky-smooth skin with the Crystal Queen of Calmness. Gently exfoliating and purely magical, crushed amethyst gemstone combines with magnesium-rich salt, ultra-nourishing organic virgin coconut oil and night-blooming jasmine sambac to lavish your body with luxe moisture.', 'Massage a handful of Body Scrub all over the skin, focusing on any dry or rough areas.\r\n\r\nLet sit for 1-2 minutes for intense moisturization. Rinse off.\r\n\r\nImmediately after bathing, apply 2-3 pumps of Body Oil all over the skin.', 'Sucrose, Magnesium Sulfate, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Capric Triglycerides, Cetearyl Olivate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Kaolin, Sorbitan Olivate, Amethyst Powder, Jasminum Sambac (Jasmine) Flower Extract, Eclipta Prostrata Extract, Melia Azadirachta Leaf Extract, Moringa Oleifera Seed Oil, Melia Azadirachta Leaf Extract, Amino Esters-1 (ex Mimosa Tenuiflora), Coccinia Indica Fruit Extract, Solanum Melongena (Eggplant) Fruit Extract', 'Inspired by the healing metaphysical properties of its namesake gemstone, Amethyst Body Scrub, infused with crushed amethyst powder, becomes a sacred component of your bathing ritual, bringing harmonizing benefits to increase your inner and outer beauty.\r\n\r\nScent: Jasmine with a hint of coconut\r\nTexture: Fine-grain scrub\r\nColor: Lilac'),
